2.caption_en: Slide summarizing the MindSphere ecosystem: an Industrial IoT platform by Siemens that connects machines and provides data-driven insights, highlighting its core value proposition, platform maturity, and stakeholder groups (business customers, implementation partners, app developers/Mendix ecosystem). The slide also shows partner and developer metrics and a source link to the MindSphere concept architecture.
